      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction: June 16 article on about unemployed gold miners in Lesotho misstated price of gold</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, an article on Tuesday about unemployed gold miners from Lesotho misstated the price of gold in 1982. According to South African industry officials, it hit a low of $280 an ounce, not $80.</p>
      </block>
